DEVELOPER TOOLS

Debugging

    make realclean # if perl Makefile.PL already run
    perl Makefile.PL -g

Profiling

    make realclean # if perl Makefile.PL already run
    perl Makefile.PL -pg

Test coverage analysis

    make realclean # if perl Makefile.PL already run
    perl Makefile.PL -cov
    make
    make testcover


